          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1716201320158-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick and with a matching lid) with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden and crisp</p><p>Once crisp, transfer the bacon to kitchen paper and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1716201324288-x200.jpg",
