      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are nearly ready, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the potatoes and mix it all together</p><p>Add the <strong>loaded base[s]</strong> and <strong>ciabatta lid[s] </strong>to the tray[s] and return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 4-5 min or until the cheese has melted</p>",
